{
  "stem": "24814.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Of course, he gets snapped up early on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was staggering and almost falling down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he insisted on sitting up with us reading X-rays and filling his role as a physician once again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was very wonderful to see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I hope he-- I hope he lived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But as we walked down the aisle-- the-- along the aisle of beds, our chief helper was a young Yugoslav surgeon, who was a prisoner himself.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But he hadn't been in long enough to be starved very much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he had an American army uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We called him 'Titto Minor,' which made him very proud.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he was a graduate of the University of Belgrade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he knew about typhus, because he-- he was part of the partisan army, the guerrillas.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Of course, they were lousy, and they-- he knew typhus when he saw it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The Americans didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They've never seen a case.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They-- so he would go along-- with typhus, you get spots.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The blood vessels rupture and they leave spots on the skin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Fleck typhus it's called, spotted typhus.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he could call the shots better than any of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He'd say, [SPEAKING GERMAN], more spots, the tongue is dry, he'll be dead tonight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The way typhus works is that the germ attacks the tiny blood vessels called capillaries, the littlest ones that you rupture when you have a nose bleed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And any part of your body.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "If it attacks in the gastrointestinal tract, you vomit blood, and you pass blood in the stool, and you die.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "If it's in the lungs, you cough blood and hemorrhage in your lung and die.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And we saw both types.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
